Package: rJST
Type: Package
Title: Joint Sentiment Topic modelling
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-09-22
Author: Max Boiten
Maintainer: Max Boiten <max_boiten@live.nl>
Description: The package runs a Joint Sentiment Topic model, as described by Lin and He, 2009.
    Currently, the model can only estimate parameters based on a corpus and not use these estimates
    for inference.
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.12),
    ggplot2,
    SnowballC,
    quanteda
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
